MACAddr - a MAC address class

Version: 0.3.0
Author: Raymond P Chudzinski
added UTF-8 support for non-ASCII vendor names

MACAddr is a class for the manipulation of IEEE MAC addresses. 
It is patterned after the IPAddr class in the Ruby core libs.
    Copyright (C) 2010 Raymond P Chudzinski

methods include comparison, determining manufacturer, printabilty and a few helpers

